<H3> <TI>   Joint Ventures Increasing In Southern Portion of Republic </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Joint Ventures Increasing In Southern Portion of Republic </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1462A Tashkent PRAVDA VOSTOKA in Russian 31 May 94 p 2 </F>
