Indicators   of Steam Turbines 

<F P=102> 947F0071B Moscow TEPLOENERGETIKA in Russian No. 1, 1994 pp 
16-22 </F>

<F P=103> 947F0071B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow TEPLOENERGETIKA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>
