<H3> <TI>   Antimicrobial Activity of Wound Discharge as Indicator of </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Antimicrobial Activity of Wound Discharge as Indicator of </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Wound   Healing 

<F P=102> 947C0249E Moscow KHIRURGIYA in Russian No. 11, Nov 93 
(manuscript received 12 Dec 91) pp 19-23 </F>

<F P=103> 947C0249E </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KHIRURGIYA </F>
